features: 【Unique Design】The orange cat plush pillow has two orange ears, two watery eyes, a sweet expression and a small tail. It comes with a surprise in her belly, 4 cute baby cats that can be removed through the zipper opening on mommy’s tummy.

【High Quality Material】The super soft fat cat plushies are made of premium plush fabrics and filled with super soft PP cotton, which makes them perfect for hugging and cuddling. So you can rest assured that this cat plush toy is safe and durable enough to keep your little one entertained.

【Perfect Gifts】Our adorable kitty plush is a good choice for birthdays, Halloween, Christmas, Thanksgiving, Valentine's Day and other gifts, loved by everyone. You can give it to your family, friends, boys, girls and lovers, they will definitely be delighted to receive the gift.

【Multipurpose】These well-made cat stuffed animals can not only be used as a decoration or sleep pillow where you want, such as a bed, office and car. The cute and healing expression and soft touch can also relieve your stress and add joy to your life.

【Warm Tips】The cat plush pillow comes in vacuum packaging, it may take 1-2 days to return to its original appearance, please be patient. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us, we will solve your problem within 24 hours.
